    <h2>Design and Quality of Content</h2>
    <p>My site incorporates the CRAP principles with a clear contrast between the background and text for readability, repetition in design elements for cohesion, alignment for a structured layout, and proximity in related content for logical grouping. The content is well-researched, focusing on Japan's travel destinations with accurate historical information and recommended spots, ensuring an engaging user experience.</p>
    
    <h2>Quantity of Content</h2>
